vote.title: A public hearing to receive comments regarding the application for and approval of the fill permit and removal of the floodplain (FP) prefix from approximately 0.19 acres of the current 1.38 acres of floodplain located at 4950 Wedgewood Lane, within the floodplain of Browning Branch, Fill Permit 20-09 - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
